<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Login OTP</title>
</head>

<body>
    <p>Hello</p>

    <p>We received a request to log in to your account associated with the email address <%= email %>.</p>

    <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) for login is: <%= otp %>
    </p>

    <p>If you did not request this login, please ignore this email.</p>

    <p>Thank you,</p>
    <p>Your App Team</p>
</body>

</html>